LibTai: 處理Holo/Hakka的程式庫

class & function name begin with LT

example:
bool LTIsValidHoloSyllable(const string& s);  

== 應該包含的功能 ==
* ASCII POJ <-> UTF-8 POJ
* Normalization
** UTF-8 POJ Normalization,  tone mark position, composing/precomposed diacritics
** ASCII POJ Normallization
** [[ConversionTable]]

== Proposed Class and Function ==
* bool LTIsValidHoloSyllable(const string& s);  

== Tone mark position ==
* Use sonority to decide the position of the tone mark
** 出現一個以上的母音的時候，調號標在sonority最高的母音上面
* Use following sonority hierarchy 
** a=ann>ou=ounn>e=enn>o=onn>i=inn>u=unn>ng>m=n
* 例
** oa2-->oá, oe2->óe, iu2->íu, iap8->ia̍p, 
